  "text": "The scarcity of the donors is the limitation of this form of treatment. Furthermore, this form of treatment is not acceptable to some women and is illegal in some countries. A further aspect of the treatment is oocyte (or embryo) cryopreservation, which is widely used for women prior to cancer treatment [CITATION_1] .",
